<P>
   FBN-49ERS-YOUNG (Stanford, Calif. _ Quarterback Steve Young, who
sat out the last 13 games of the 49ers' season after sustaining
back-to-back concussions, will probably be cleared medically to
play in 2000, his agent said. By JOHN CRUMPACKER.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-SHRINE-BOWL (Stanford, Calif.) _ Quick question: Who won
last year's Shrine Bowl?
</P>
<P>
   Quick answer: Who really cares?
</P>
<P>
   That one team actually wins and another loses is among the more
insignificant factors of the Shrine Bowl, which isn't about winning
or losing as much as it's about exposure for kids trying to reach
the next level. By JOHN SHEA.
</P>
