<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    HAITIANS CHEERS OVER DECISION TO REJOIN KIDS WITH MOM, MUTED BY
CRIES OVER DISPARITIES WITH CUBAN IMMIGRANT TREATMENT
 &HT;    By MIKE WILLIAMS 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
