<P>
   &UR; COMMENT (k) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   NYHAN-COLUMN (Undated) -- No Massachusetts politician more
epitomized character in public life than Elliot Lee Richardson, the
rectitudinous Yankee lost to a brain hemorrhage on New Year's Eve
at 79. By David Nyhan.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; LIFESTYLE &LR;   &UR; (l) &LR;
</P>
