all-new Audi S4 Quattro, a high-performance version of Audi's
entry-level A4 compact sedan. The S4 isn't for everyone; it's a bit
pricey at $37,900 (plus transportation and options), quite a bit
higher than the price of the base A4 1.8T, which lists for just
$23,990. So what makes the S4 worth $14,000 more? After all, you
could buy the A4 1.8T and add a nice Honda Civic or Toyota Corolla
for the extra 14 grand, and have two cars instead of one. By G.
CHAMBERS WILLIAMS III. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle
category. &QL; 
