making computer memory chips, consumer electronics and automobiles,
South Korea has set its sights on a far loftier goal: conquering
outer space. The government plans to develop a rocket capable of
ferrying satellites into orbit within the next five years. By
Calvin Sims. (The story has moved in ``i'' news file.) 1,300 words.
</P>
