<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-14 19:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6483 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-SAFRICA-TOURISM-ART-2     01-14 1301
