the failed school construction project in South Gate. The money --
possibly as much as $39 million -- was spent to buy the tainted 38
parcels of land. Officials with the Prop BB oversight committee are
expected to attempt to recoup the money from the school district.
By Greg Gittrich (Will move on the ``n'' California and ``a''
national news wires.)
