<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-14 20:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6508 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-BRADLEY-IMAGE-ART-2TA     01-14 1173
