<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-14 21:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6570 &Cx1f; tth-z
r v BC-BUDGET-SPI &LR;      01-14 0068
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BUDGET-SPI </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the following
